            "body": "Thanks,\r\n\r\nBTW this dos not only impact abduco, this also impacts dtach - which does the same assumptions in sigwinch redraw mode:\r\n\r\nsteps to reproduce:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\ndtach -A /tmp/test -r winch -e '^G' nvim\r\n```\r\ntype `^G`\r\nthen relaunch previous command.\r\n",
