        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "FYI\r\n\r\non `diss` (dtach like program), to workaround this issue, on client side, here is what I did:\r\n\r\nbefore detaching, send TIOCSWINSZ with width- 1, height - 1\r\n\r\nThat way when re-attaching + sending TIOCSWINSZ + SIGWINCH, nvim detects a change in size and reacts to sigwinch\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/yazgoo/diss/commit/fd75b152acd926955b58a45d993291d3264c18fa",
